# This directory holds EVL Dovetail patch files (*.patch).
# Patches are generated via scripts/patch/gen-patch.sh or downloaded
# from the EVL mailing list. See docs/porting-notes.md for details.
#
# Naming convention:
#   0001-evl-riscv-dovetail-base.patch
#   0002-evl-riscv-fpu-context.patch
#   0003-evl-k1-clocksource.patch
#   ...
